# Project: Film Society Website with Next.js 15 + Sanity + TypeScript

# Brand Guidelines Implementation

## Project Context

This is a Next.js 15 website for St. Augustine Film Society, a cultural institution focused on independent cinema. The project uses Sanity CMS for content management, TypeScript for type safety, and Tailwind CSS for styling. The design should reflect the historic charm of St. Augustine while maintaining modern web standards.

## Technical Stack

- Next.js 15 with App Router
- TypeScript (strict mode)
- Sanity CMS with embedded studio
- Tailwind CSS v3 (stable)
- pnpm package manager
- TMDB API integration for film data

