## Color Usage Guidelines

- **PRIMARY BACKGROUNDS**: Always use Sandstone (#F7F2E6)
- **PRIMARY TEXT**: Always use Charcoal (#333333) on light backgrounds
- **HERO SECTIONS**: Use Terracotta (#BF5B3D) for prominence
- **FEATURED CONTENT**: Use Ocean Blue (#2B5B7D) for films, icons, navigation
- **RATINGS/AWARDS**: Use Ochre (#E3A85B) exclusively for star ratings and awards
- **NEVER** use colors outside this palette without explicit approval

## Typography Guidelines

- **Headings**: Playfair Display or similar classic serif (font-display)
- **Body Text**: Inter or similar readable sans-serif (font-body)
- **Film Titles**: Always italicized in content
- **Responsive Sizing**: Mobile-first approach with proper hierarchy

## Component Architecture

- Use TypeScript interfaces for all props
- Implement proper error boundaries
- Follow Next.js 15 App Router patterns
- Use Sanity's GROQ for data fetching
- Ensure mobile-first responsive design

## Content Guidelines

- **Film Titles**: Italicized, include director and year on first mention
- **Dates**: Format as "August 15, 2025 at 7:00 PM EDT"
- **Numbers**: Spell out 1-9, use numerals for 10+
- **Grammar**: American English with Oxford comma
- **Accessibility**: Alt text for all images, proper contrast ratios

## Icon System (Lucide React)

### Navigation Icons

- **Play**: Film screenings, trailers, video content (color: ocean-blue)
- **Heart**: Favorites, likes, saving content (color: terracotta)
- **Ticket**: Ticket purchases, events (color: ochre)
- **Users**: Membership, community (color: ocean-blue)

### Content Icons

- **Film**: Movie details, collections (color: ocean-blue)
- **Star**: Ratings, reviews (color: ochre)
- **Camera**: Behind-scenes, director profiles (color: ocean-blue)
- **BookOpen**: Articles, blog posts (color: charcoal)
- **Award**: Festival awards, recognition (color: ochre)

### Contact Icons

- **MapPin**: Venue locations (color: terracotta)
- **Phone**: Contact numbers (color: charcoal)
- **Mail**: Email addresses (color: charcoal)
- **Home**: Address, main page (color: ocean-blue)

